    "section_text_h6wLD9": {
      "type": "section-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_DXcrcw": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our Fabric<\/p>",
            "size": 100,
            "heading_highlight_type": "underline-hand-drawn",
            "highlight_color": "#000000",
            "highlight_text_color": ""
          }
        },
        "subheading_TCYyVh": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>better for your skin, planet, and coochie.<\/p>",
            "size": 145,
            "margin_bottom": 16
          }
        },
        "text_XVGdBL": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Cherri's core collection is made of a customized blend of Supima® Cotton, LENZING™ Modal, and a little bit of spandex for the perfect amount of stretch and softness.<br\/><br\/>Our suppliers are certified Standard 100 by OEKO-TEX®, meaning no toxic stuff touching your intimate areas.<\/p>",
            "size": 100
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_DXcrcw",
        "subheading_TCYyVh",
        "text_XVGdBL"
      ],
      "name": "Text",
      "settings": {
        "text_position": "center",
        "bg_color_secondary": false,
        "text_color": "text-dark",
        "width": "wrapper--narrow",
        "padding_top": 60,
        "padding_bottom": 60
      }
    },
    "cdb3be2a-9d5e-47f0-9431-04f739f3c7cc": {
      "type": "section-image-with-text",
      "settings": {
        "section_height": "three-fifty-height",
        "layout": "overlay",
        "image_location": "left",
        "image_width": "extra-narrow",
        "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Lavender_Hill_jersey_fabric.webp",
        "subheading": "the world's finest cotton",
        "title": "<p>Supima® Cotton<\/p>",
        "heading_highlight_type": "highlight-color",
        "highlight_color": "#d43747",
        "highlight_text_color": "#e90000",
        "heading_size": 130,
        "content": "<p><strong>What makes Supima better than other forms of cotton? <\/strong><\/p><ul><li>It's extra-long staple fibre is luxuriously softer and stronger than other forms of cotton.<\/li><li>Supply chain traceability, agricultural technology, and soil health management ensure quality and low environmental impact.<\/li><li>Supima uses sustainable cultivation practices, including efficient water use to be better for the environment.<\/li><li>It represents less than 1% of the world's cotton - making it a rare luxury.<\/li><li>It is only grown in the USA.<\/li><li>It is OEKO-TEX® Certified, which verifies that the product is free from harmful substances (like PFAS and GMOS)<\/li><\/ul>",
        "text_alignment": "left",
        "button_text": "",
        "button_link": "",
        "button_color": "btn--black",
        "button_style": "btn--solid",
        "button_size": "btn--small",
